data.description: Location Location! Come check out this beautiful end unit K. Hovinian home. Featuring tons of natural light, high ceilings, updated fixtures, and a location that you just can't beat, this home will not disappoint. One of my favorite features about this home is the flex room on the first floor that can be used as an office, home gym, or spare bedroom. The large, pet friendly yard is so hard to find inside the loop! It is also the perfect space for entertaining, grilling, and making memories. Did I mention that it is FULLY turfed for low maintenance?! Schedule your showing ASAP. This home will not last long! No flooding!
